title: Zucchini
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegetarian-friendly take away with small sitting section, operating since 2008. Menu includes muesli, in-house-made jam on bread, vegetarian platter, chickpea burger,  Loop St. is parallel to Long St. On the corner of Longmarket St near the Christian Barnard medical centre. Confirmed opened by owner, Jan 2013.
